{
  "stem": "19111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually, we were building the outer shell of the factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had-- what it looked like was a big mountain of gravel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then over the gravel was iron rods.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they were pouring concrete over them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also the foundations-- we were pouring concrete.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The concrete was going day and night on a 24-hour basis without stopping.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were put into the-- into the-- into-- to do the work while-- helping the concrete run into the right place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to stand and stomp it with certain long poles, and carry the iron rods, and connect them-- the rods.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the work itself was difficult and hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "However, the Nazis were rushing us constantly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were constantly beating us with electric, electric wires-- electric cables, pieces of electric cable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were beating us over the heads in order to expedite and rush us all the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were, like, on a-- on a mission to destroy us and rushing the factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was mayhem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had-- every morning we went to work, we had to carry with us-- at the end of the-- of, of the march-- at the end of the people, there was a wagon-- two wagons, actually, without a horse.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had to carry-- a few people had to pull the wagons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And those wagons were so that every single day when we were coming back to camp, people who have died in the interim were put on the wagons and were brought back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was a daily routine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They-- food has diminished as they-- time went on, and-- until they were just given a little piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They-- the morality of the people was completely shattered to pieces.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
